## Gilfoyle — 3 accounts, Hooli Bank
##########################################################################

### [gilfoyle] List all accounts
GET https://au-api.basiq.io/users/{{gilfoyle.userId}}/accounts
accept: application/json
authorization: Bearer {{serverToken}}

### [gilfoyle] Retrieve Hooli Awards Card (Visa)
GET https://au-api.basiq.io/users/{{gilfoyle.userId}}/accounts/{{gilfoyle.accounts.visa}}
accept: application/json
authorization: Bearer {{serverToken}}

### [gilfoyle] Retrieve Hooli Access (Transaction)
GET https://au-api.basiq.io/users/{{gilfoyle.userId}}/accounts/{{gilfoyle.accounts.access}}
accept: application/json
authorization: Bearer {{serverToken}}

### [gilfoyle] Retrieve Hooli Saver (Savings)
GET https://au-api.basiq.io/users/{{gilfoyle.userId}}/accounts/{{gilfoyle.accounts.saver}}
accept: application/json
authorization: Bearer {{serverToken}}

### [gilfoyle] Transactions — all accounts
GET https://au-api.basiq.io/users/{{gilfoyle.userId}}/transactions?limit=500
accept: application/json
