### [gilfoyle] Transactions — Visa
GET https://au-api.basiq.io/users/{{gilfoyle.userId}}/transactions?filter=account.id.eq('{{gilfoyle.accounts.visa}}')&limit=500
accept: application/json
authorization: Bearer {{serverToken}}

### [gilfoyle] Transactions — Access
GET https://au-api.basiq.io/users/{{gilfoyle.userId}}/transactions?filter=account.id.eq('{{gilfoyle.accounts.access}}')&limit=500
accept: application/json
authorization: Bearer {{serverToken}}

### [gilfoyle] Transactions — Saver
GET https://au-api.basiq.io/users/{{gilfoyle.userId}}/transactions?filter=account.id.eq('{{gilfoyle.accounts.saver}}')&limit=500
accept: application/json
authorization: Bearer {{serverToken}}
